The paper discusses the performance of Graphcore's IPU Processor for deep neural networks used in image-based applications. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions machine learning models and benchmarking, which are relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The mention of energy efficiency could also suggest cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) as a possible sub-category. Finally, the mention of training and inference could suggest cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as another possible sub-category.
